data.name: label62.ToolTip
data.value:
Current combination of Country/State/City settings. Will match to any airport that has one of the listed country, state or city strings in "runways.xml" file.
To modify filters in current combination select the Country/State/City item in the respective field and press "Enter" to add it or "Delete" to remove it from the combination favourite.

data.name: ComboBoxGeneralLocationFavourites.ToolTip
data.value:
Select the combination of Country, State and City filters to be used in identifying runways for use in a scenario.
To modify filters in current combination select the Country/State/City item in the respective field and press "Enter" to add it or "Delete" to remove it from the combination favourite.
To rename a favourite, type in the new name and press "Enter", this will rename the existing favourite and create a new favourite with the old favourite name.
To delete a favourite, press "Delete" with the "Favourites" field name selected.
To see the currently selected favourite, mouseover the "Filters" field below.

data.name: ComboBoxGeneralLocationCity.ToolTip
data.value:
To add selected city to currently selected "Favourites" press "Enter" To delete selected city from currently selected "Favourites" press "Delete"
Make sure you click with the mouse in the field or change the selection via the dropdown to ensure the field is in focus.
Selecting a city without then pressing enter or delete has no effect on the currently selected favourite. Scenarios are generated based ONLY on the filter values in the currently selected favourite.
Select "None" and press "Enter" to clear runway selection filters based on city in currently selected favourite.
